These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower, azalea
1. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Flower   | amaryllis | sunflower | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, amber, blood-red
1. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes blood-red is in the middle##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Color   | turquise | blood-red | amber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: german, indonesian, chinese
1. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3
2. the chinese is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Nationality   | indonesian | german | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
City: berlin, venice, hamburg
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| City   | berlin | venice | hamburg |

