.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
3 different games are played: chess, go, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
2. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |   3    |
| Game   | chess | go | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, climbing, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Sport   | cricket | climbing | water-polo |

